PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Product Discovery App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the app find new products?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app uses advanced algorithms to scour the internet and identify the latest product launches across various categories. We analyze data from e-commerce sites, social media, blogs, and more to bring you the freshest product offerings.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What types of products can I find?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app covers a wide range of product categories, including electronics, fashion, home goods, beauty, and more. Whether you're looking for the hottest new gadget or the trendiest fashion item, we've got you covered.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How often is the app updated?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We update our product database continuously to ensure you have access to the latest and greatest products as soon as they hit the market. Our app refreshes multiple times per day to keep you in the loop.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I filter or sort the products?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! Our app allows you to filter products by category, price range, release date, and more. You can also sort the results based on your preferences, such as popularity, price, or release date.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How often is the product catalog updated?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Our product catalog is continuously updated to ensure you have access to the latest offerings. New products are added daily, so you'll always find something fresh and exciting to explore.
